      <title>Simple calculations with Vim's expression register</title>
      <description>&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;The &amp;lt;a href=&amp;quot;http://vimdoc.sourceforge.net/htmldoc/change.html#quote=&amp;quot;&amp;gt;expression register&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt; lets us evaluate a snippet of Vimscript code. This is handy when you need to perform simple calculations and insert the result into the document.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;

</description>
      <enclosure url="http://media.vimcasts.org/videos/56/expression-register.m4v" length="8247836" type="video/x-m4v"/>
