      <description>&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;In case you hadn't noticed, Vimcasts.org is back from hibernation! I'm publishing new screencasts and blog posts regularly. If you can't keep up with the &amp;lt;a href=&amp;quot;http://vimcasts.org/feeds&amp;quot;&amp;gt;RSS feeds&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt;, or via &amp;lt;a href=&amp;quot;http://twitter.com/vimcasts&amp;quot;&amp;gt;Twitter&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt;, then you might want to &amp;lt;a href=&amp;quot;http://eepurl.com/w5A7P&amp;quot;&amp;gt;subscribe to the Vimcasts.org newsletter&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt;. I'll send an email digest once a month containing links to all of the material published over the course of the previous month.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;

